oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jimmy Dee Show with Linda Flanigan and Rich Mounce
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Dee, Jimmy, 1937-2011; Flanigan, Linda; Mounce, Rich; Offset printing
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white negatives taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising The Jimmy Dee Show with Linda Flanigan, Rich Mounce, and the Country Editions. The negative features photographs of Jimmy Dee, Linda Flanigan, and Rich Mounce. The bottom portion of the negative, which usually contains information on the talent agency, has been cut out and is missing. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
